			<h3 class="first"><a href="#p3898">Change taskbar appearance?</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=3898#p3898"><img src="./styles/prosilver/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=1453">Lupuss</a></strong> &raquo; Mon Mar 29, 2010 1:16 pm </p>

			

			<div class="content">Hi everyone.<br /><br />I'd like to know if there's any way to change the taskbar appearance to match the selected theme. I haven't seen that option anywhere though.<br /><br />Thanks</div>

			

		</div>

		
			<dl class="postprofile" id="profile3898">
